{{Infobox Sport governing body |assocname= Croatian Canoe Federation |logo= |sport= [[Canoeing]] |abbrev = |founded = 1939 |aff = [[International Canoe Federation]] |affdate = |region = [[European Canoe Association]] |regionyear = |president = [[Marko Ćurković]] |secretary = |coach = |womenscoach = |url = http://www.kajak.hr/ |countryflag= Croatia }}
The '''Croatian Canoe Federation''' ({{lang-hr|Hrvatski kajakaški savez}}) is the governing body of [[rowing (sport)|rowing]] in [[Croatia]]. It organizes the Croatian representation at international competitions and the Croatian National Championships.
The Federation was formed on August 6, 1939 in [[Zagreb]].<ref name="HKS">[http://www.kajak.hr/hrvatski/tijela.php Bodies of the Federation]</ref> It became a member of the [[International Canoe Federation]] in 1992 and of the [[European Canoe Association]] in 1993.<ref name="HKS"/>
